                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>wish, and I shall be happy to do anything in my<lb/> power to serve you.</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Dr. Fishel</persName> lectured to day to about a dozen\n\t\t\t\tor<lb/> two persons. The “Temple” however was crowded<lb/> when <persName><hi\n\t\t\t\t\t\trend=\"underline\">Dr.</hi> Adler</persName> held forth.</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(1)\">The new <sic>Portugese</sic> synagogue in <placeName>19<hi\n\t\t\t\t\t\trend=\"sup\">th</hi> St</placeName> is<lb/> progressing, the front is entirely\n\t\t\t\tup, and<lb/> presents a splendid appearance.</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(1)\">Shall we have the pleasure of seeing you<lb/> here this year?</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(1)\">My parents desire to be kindly remembered.<lb/> Father is suffering\n\t\t\t\twith his old complaint and<lb/> mother is not very well.</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(1)\">With best wishes for your health and<lb/> with continued feelings of\n\t\t\t\tthe highest esteem and<lb/> friendly regard I remain Dr. Sir</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(4)\">Very truly yours</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n\t\t\t\t<persName role=\"author\">J. Solis Ritterband</persName>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t<placeName>No. 10 Wall St</placeName>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p>and</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t<placeName>\n\t\t\t\t\t<hi rend=\"underline\">80 Charles St</hi>\n\t\t\t\t</placeName>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n\t\t\t\t<addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n\t\t\t\t<placeName>Philada.</placeName>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t</body>\n\t</text>\n</TEI>"
